     <body>
     <div type="encomium">
   <pb facs="5"/>
   <head>To the Author.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>HOw e're thou maist by blazing all <hi>Abuse,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>Incurre suspect, thou speak'st what thou hast prou'd,</l>
      <l>(Tho then to keepe it close it thee behou'd,</l>
      <l>S<gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>, <hi>Reason</hi> makes for thee a iust excuse)</l>
      <l>Yet of thy paines, the <hi>B<gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1 letter">
               <desc>•</desc>
            </gap>st</hi> may make good vse,</l>
      <l>Then of the <hi>Best,</hi> thy paines should be approu'd,</l>
      <l>And for the same of them shouldst be belou'd.</l>
      <l>Sith thou of <hi>Falsehoods Floud</hi> d<gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>'st ope the <hi>Sluce,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>That they at wast<gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap> continually may runne,</l>
      <l>By she wing men <gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>he <hi>R<gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1 letter">
               <desc>•</desc>
            </gap>aches</hi> that they haue,</l>
      <l>That honest men may so or'e-reach a <hi>Knaue,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>Or <gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>ound their swallowing <hi>Deepes,</hi> the same to shunne:</l>
      <l>But if from hence, a <hi>Knaue</hi> more cunning growes,</l>
      <l>That <hi>Spider</hi> sucks but poison from thy <hi>Rose.</hi>
      </l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>
         <hi>Thy friend if thine owne,</hi>
Io: Da:</signed>
   </closer>
